SQL_STMT_U.val: select CFLC_USRID,CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED,CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED,IMQD_IMQH_TYPE,IMQD_LINENO from :1/CFLC join :1/IMQD on CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED=IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO and CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED= IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO and IMQD_IMQH_TYPE=:2 and IMQD_DATEANSWER is null where CFLC_USRID=':3' and CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED*1000000000 + CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED*10000 + IMQD_LINENO >:4 :5 order by CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED,CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED,IMQD_LINENO

select CFLC_USRID,CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED,CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED,IMQD_IMQH_TYPE,IMQD_LINENO from :1/CFLC join :1/IMQD on CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED=IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO and CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED= IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO and IMQD_IMQH_TYPE=:2 and IMQD_DATEANSWER is null where CFLC_USRID=':3' :4 order by CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED,CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED,IMQD_LINENO
